d October 19, 2015)</ref>\n! style=\"width:30px;\"|<small>[[Independent Albums|US Ind]]</small>\n|-\n| 2009\n| '''''[[Gallop Meets the Earth]]'''''\n*Released: September 29, 2009\n*Label: Underground Operations\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 299\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 47\n|}\n\n[[File:ProtestTheHero2007-2.jpg|right|thumb|250px|live in Burlington, May 2007]]\n\n===Compilation appearances===\n*''(Coles) Notes from the Underground'' (2002) <small>(\"Break the Chain\" and \"Asperity of Sin\")</small>\n*''Greetings from the Underground'' (2004) <small>(\"Soft Targets Dig Softer Graves\")</small>\n*''Things Could Be Worse'' (2004) <small>(\"Break the Chain\")</small>\n*''Orange and Grey'' (2005, DVD) <small>(\"Silent Genocide,\" \"These Colours Don't Run,\" \"Red Stars Over the Battle of the Cowshed\" and \" and Loathing In Laramie\")</small><ref>[http://www.punkbands.com/news/3853/ \"Orange And Grey Compilation DVD Released\"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090827062157/http://www.punkbands.com/news/3853/ |date=2009-08-27 }} PunkBands.com. Retrieved on May 26, 2009.</ref>\n*''The Power of Music'' (2005) <small>(\"An Apathetic New World\")</small>\n*''Warped Tour 2006 Compilation'' (2006) <small>(\"Heretics and Killers\")</small>\n\n===Music videos===\n{|class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Song\n! Director\n|-\n| 2003\n| \"These Colours Don't Run\"\n| rowspan=\"3\"| Marc Ricciardelli\n|-\n| 2005\n| \"Blindfolds Aside\"\n|-\n| 2006\n| \"Heretics and Killers\"\n|-\n| 2007\n| \"The Divine Suicide of K\"\n| Colin Minihan\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2008\n| \"Bloodmeat\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Marc Andre Debruyne\n|-\n| \"[[Sequoia Throne]]\"\n|-\n| \"Palms Read\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Sean Michael Turrell\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2009\n| \"Spoils\"\n|-\n| \"Limb From Limb\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Marc Andre Debruyne\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2011\n| \"C'est la Vie\"\n|-\n| \"Hair-Trigger\"\n| Marc Ricciardelli\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2013\n| \"Clarity\"\n|Kenneth Wilcox & Todd 